<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head></head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f7; color: #333333; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <div style="width: 90%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px;">
        <div style="text-align: center">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/miscellaneous/image/upload/v1729975173/akeurope/logo-full.png"
                style="height: 35px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px" alt="akeurope.org Logo" />
        </div>
        <p style="color: #333333; line-height: 1.3rem;">Dear {{name}},</p>
        <p style="color: #333333; line-height: 1.3rem;">Assalam o Alaikum,</p>
        <p style="color: #333333; line-height: 1.3rem;">
            We hope this message finds you in the best of health and faith.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #333333; line-height: 1.3rem;">
            We wanted to provide you with an important update regarding the current situation in Gaza and its impact on
            our operations. Due to the ongoing conflict and severe disruption in telephone and internet services, there
            have been delays in our regular reporting for sponsored beneficiaries.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #333333; line-height: 1.3rem;">
            Tragically, just two days ago, one of our dedicated team members in Gaza, <i>Deema Mosleh</i>, lost her
            father in an airstrike by Israeli forces. Our hearts go out to her and all those suffering during this
            difficult time.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #333333; line-height: 1.3rem;">
            Despite these challenges, we are actively maintaining communication with our team on the ground via their
            telephone numbers and are working diligently to ensure that all pending reports are completed and shared as
            soon as conditions allow.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #333333; line-height: 1.3rem;">
            We sincerely appreciate your patience and understanding as we navigate through these turbulences.
        </p>
        {{#unless tooManyEntries}}
        <p style="color: #333333; line-height: 1.3rem;">
            {{#if pluralEntries}}
            Following children in Gaza are linked to your email address. {{#if newUser}}You can view detailed profile in the <a style="color: #333333; text-decoration: underline;" href="{{portalUrl}}">customer portal</a>.{{/if}}
            {{else}}
            Following child in Gaza is linked to your email address. {{#if newUser}} You can view detailed profile in the <a style="color: #333333; text-decoration: underline;" href="{{portalUrl}}">customer portal</a>.{{/if}}
            {{/if}}
        </p>
        <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 15px;">
            <thead>
                <tr style="background-color: #f5f5f5;">
                    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #dddddd;">Child</th>
                    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #dddddd;">Age</th>
                    <th style="text-align: right; padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #dddddd;">Location</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {{#each entries}}
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; color: #333333;">{{this.name}}</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; text-align: left; color: #333333;">{{this.age}}</td>
                    <td style="padding: 8px; text-align: right; color: #333333;">{{this.cluster}} Gaza</td>
                </tr>
                {{/each}}
            </tbody>
        </table>
        {{/unless}}
        
        <p style="color: #333333; line-height: 1.3rem;">
            With gratitude,<br>The Alkhidmat Europe Team <br> <a href="https://akeurope.org"
                style="text-decoration: none; color: #007A78">akeurope.org</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>